{"FOP":[{"def":"One whose ambition it is to gain admiration by showy dress; a coxcomb; an inferior dandy.","pos":""}],"FOP-DOODLE":[{"def":"A stupid or insignaficant fellow; a fool; a simpleton.","pos":""}],"FOPPERY":[{"def":"The behavior, dress, or other indication of a fop; coxcombry; affectation of show; showy folly.","pos":""}],"FOPPISH":[{"def":"Foplike; characteristic of a top in dress or manners; making an ostentatious display of gay clothing; affected in manners.","pos":""}]}